            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## DockPops Companion 1.2

- Fixed the closed poplet icon recipe so unopened poplets no longer get the fat white border around their Dock icon.
- Enabled Sparkle automatic update checks so installed companions can discover new releases without relying only on manual checks.
- Preserved the companion-managed live icon mirror path so regenerated poplets keep using the prompt-free icon source.
]]></description>
